nodes.text: By the time of the Cold War, a proxy conflict between the reconstituted Sith Empire and Galactic Republic, a gruesome battle had been fought, between the Warriors of Shadow and the cult Knell of Muspilli, on a nameless moon. Eventually, someone was sent to study the battle's wreckage that had been left behind, discovering an artifact of one of the cults buried within one of their derelict starships.
